Package: FileDialogs
Type: Package
Title: Opens a data frame using the OS File Dialog.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rodrigo Pinto Coelho
Maintainer: Rodrigo Pinto Coelho <rodrigopcoelho@hotmail.com>
Description: The GetFile function from the package FileDialogs opens
    an OS File Dilalog to let you choose a file of several different
    formats to be imported into a dataframe, data.table or arrow table.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
  shiny (>= 0.13),
  miniUI (>= 0.1.1),
  rstudioapi (>= 0.5),
  rio (>= 0.5.16),
  data.table (>= 1.12.6),
  arrow (>= 0.15.1.1)
